item.name: SUPERSTAR SHOES
item.productTitle: ADIDAS SUPERSTAR SHOES ARE MADE OF RECYCLED MATERIALS.
item.productSubtitle: Same look. The same feeling. Other materials. The Adidas Superstar shoes have been constantly evolving since their launch in the 1970s. It adapts to new needs and global changes. These shoes may not save the planet on their own, but they are definitely a step in the right direction. They are made of recycled materials, natural and renewable rubber, and have a synthetic leather upper. And that's a good start. This model contains functional recycled Primegreen materials. 70% of the upper is made of recycled material. No new polyester.
